verbose_text: In line with the reduced cell infiltration, expression of intercellular adhesion molecule (Icam) and vascular cell adhesion protein (Vcam), tumor necrosis factor-alpha (Tnf-alpha) and interleukin-18 (Il-18), C-C motif ligand 5 (Ccl5), C-X-C motif ligand 1 (Cxcl1), and C-X-C motif ligand 2 (Cxcl2) were significantly reduced in the livers of Ldlr -/- Siglec-G -/- mice compared to Ldlr -/- mice (XREF_FIG C).
